imageAssets.description: Warm, inviting hero image for a honey farm website. Golden hour sunlight filtering through trees onto a picturesque Sooke landscape (coastal British Columbia feel, lush greenery). In the foreground, neatly arranged beehives with bees subtly active. A sense of peace and natural abundance. Colors: dominant natural greens, golden sunlight, blue sky hints. Style: photorealistic, slightly dreamy.
imageAssets.purpose: Main hero banner for website homepage (#home section).

imageAssets.description: Authentic, friendly image for 'About Us' section. Two people (representing beekeepers, can be diverse, age 30s-50s) in partial beekeeping gear (e.g., veils up, or just casual outdoor attire), smiling warmly, standing near well-maintained beehives on a sunny day. Background shows a glimpse of a charming Sooke farm or lush garden. Focus on approachability and passion. Colors: natural greens, browns, blues, with pops of color from flowers. Style: naturalistic digital art.
imageAssets.purpose: Image for the 'About Us' section, conveying personality and connection to the land.

imageAssets.description: Artistic still life of honey products. Several glass jars of varying sizes filled with rich, golden amber honey. One jar could be slightly open with a honey dipper resting on it. Include elements like fresh honeycomb, a few sprigs of local Sooke wildflowers (e.g., fireweed, clover), and perhaps a rustic wooden surface. Soft, natural lighting. Colors: rich golds, ambers, greens, and whites. Style: photorealistic, food photography aesthetic.

Engaging action shot for 'Beekeeping Experience'. A small group of people (2-3) in full white beekeeping suits and veils, attentively observing a beekeeper (also in full suit) holding up a frame covered in bees. Focus on the sense of discovery and safe interaction. Sunny day, green apiary background. Style: photorealistic, bright and inviting.
imageAssets.purpose: Primary image for 'Beekeeping Experience Days' section, possibly for a carousel.

imageAssets.description: Another angle for 'Beekeeping Experience'. Close-up on a gloved hand gently holding a honeycomb frame, with bees visible. Highlights the detail and beauty of the hive. Soft focus background. Style: photorealistic, detailed macro.
imageAssets.purpose: Supporting image for 'Beekeeping Experience Days' section, possibly for a carousel.

imageAssets.description: Cozy and unique interior of the 'Sleep Over Beehives' Airbnb. A well-lit room with a comfortable bed, bee-themed decor (e.g., honeycomb patterned throw, bee artwork). Colors: warm neutrals, accents of gold and soft green. Style: photorealistic, interior design photography.
imageAssets.purpose: Main image for the 'Airbnb - Sleep Over Beehives' section, possibly for a carousel.
